## ✨ Features

### 👨‍💻 Portfolio Website
- Modern responsive user interface  
- Clean portfolio sections  
- Smooth scrolling navigation  
- Interactive animations  
- Mobile-friendly design  
- Dark/Light mode support  

---

### 📩 Contact System
- Functional contact form  
- Real-time message submission  
- MongoDB message storage  
- Email notifications using Resend API  
- Form validation and error handling  

---

### 🛠 Admin Dashboard
- View all incoming messages  
- Delete messages  
- Mark messages as read  
- Dynamic unread message counter  
- Real-time updates without refreshing  

---

### 🔔 Real-Time Features
- Live notifications using Socket.IO  
- Instant message synchronization  
- Real-time delete updates  
- Admin dashboard auto-refresh  

---

### 📧 Communication Features
- One-click Gmail reply system  
- Quick contact integration  
- Professional contact management  

