## 🏗 System Architecture

```text
Frontend (React + Vite)
        ↓
REST API Requests
        ↓
Node.js + Express Backend
        ↓
MongoDB Database
        ↓
Socket.IO Real-Time Events
        ↓
Admin Dashboard Updates